text:
Umm...
Maybe the beginning here isn't going well.

Let's go back...
One more time!

S-Sorry... Naa-chan... We were supposed
to watch the dance video together...

It's okay~
You looked super cute sleeping, Tenka-chan.

Aah... Naa-chan...
were you watching the video the whole time...?

Yeah, just a bit. But hey,
maybe I've picked up something useful from it.
So, shall we do it again tomorrow?
